cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.SD 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of "cs.CL" (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and sentence simplification. It may also belong to "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence) and "cs.LG" (Machine Learning) as it proposes an unsupervised approach to sentence simplification. Additionally, it could be categorized under "cs.NE" (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it uses neural networks for semantic representation. Finally, it could be classified under "cs.SD" (Sound) as it deals with the soundness of the proposed approach.
